## Additional Terms for Blockchain Components

This project includes smart contracts and blockchain-related code that interact
with the Cardano blockchain. Users are responsible for:

1. Understanding the risks associated with blockchain transactions
2. Ensuring compliance with local regulations regarding cryptocurrency and blockchain technology
3. Properly securing their private keys and wallet credentials
4. Testing all smart contract interactions on testnets before mainnet deployment

