This software is provided for educational and development purposes. Users should
conduct thorough testing and security audits before deploying to production
environments, especially when handling real assets or managing IoT devices that
control physical security systems.

The developers and contributors are not responsible for any loss of funds,
security breaches, or damages resulting from the use of this software.
